      <h4 class="page-header" id="retrieve">Retrieve a conversation</h4>
      <p>Retrieves the details of an existing conversation. You need only supply the unique bot and conversation identifier that was returned upon conversation creation.</p>

      <pre>curl https://api.dialoganalytics.com/v1/b/:id/conversations/:id</pre>

      <h4 class="page-header" id="list">List all conversations</h4>
      <p>Returns a list of the bot's conversations. The conversations are returned sorted by creation date, with the most recent conversations appearing first.</p>

      <pre>curl https://api.dialoganalytics.com/v1/b/:id/conversations</pre>
